quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  51,24,Ese wamenye iby’inkuru y’abashyitsi ba Aburahamu b’abanyacyubahiro
  51,25,"Ubwo binjiraga iwe bakavuga bati \"Salamu (Amahoro nabe kuri mwe!)\" Nuko akavuga ati \"Salamu, bantu batazwi"
  51,26,"Nuko arinyabya asanga ab’iwe, azana inyama z’inyana yokeje"
  51,27,"Maze arazibegereza, (abonye batarambura amaboko ngo barye) aravuga ati \"Ese ntabwo murya"
  51,28,"Nuko arabishisha (abonye batariye). Baravuga bati \"Witinya!\" Hanyuma bamuha inkuru nziza (yo kuzabyara umwana) w’umuhungu uzaba afite ubumenyi (ku bijyanye na Allah)"
  51,29,"Nuko umugore we aza yiyamira, akubita agashyi mu buranga bwe (atangara), aravuga ati \"Umukecuru w’urubereri"
  51,30,"Baravuga bati \"Uko ni ko Nyagasani wawe yavuze. Mu by’ukuri, ni Ushishoza, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  51,31,"(Aburahamu) aravuga ati \"None ni iki kibagenza yemwe (ba malayika) mwoherejwe mwe"
  51,32,"Baravuga bati \"Rwose twoherejwe ku bantu b’inkozi z’ibibi"
  51,33,Kugira ngo tubamanurireho amabuye y’ibumba (ryo mu muriro)
  51,34,"(Ayo mabuye) yashyizweho ibimenyetso na Nyagasani wawe, akaba ari igihano ku barengera (imbago za Allah)"
  51,35,Nuko abemeramana (bari mu mudugudu w’inkozi z’ibibi) tuwubakuramo (kugira ngo ibihano bitabageraho)
  51,36,Ariko nta n’abo twasanzemo uretse urugo rumwe rw’umwemeramana (Intumwa Loti)
  51,37,Nuko (nyuma yo kuwurimbura) tuwusigamo ikimenyetso ku batinya ibihano bibabaza
  51,38,"No mu nkuru ya Musa (harimo isomo), ubwo twamwoherezaga kwa Farawo tumuhaye ibimenyetso n’ububasha bigaragara"
  51,39,"Ariko Farawo yishingikirije ububasha yari afite, atera umugongo (yanga kwemera ubutumwa yari azaniwe), aravuga ati \"Uyu ni umurozi cyangwa umusazi"
  51,40,Nuko tumufatana n’ingabo ze maze tubajugunya mu nyanja kandi agayitse (kubera ibikorwa bye by’ubuhakanyi)
  51,41,"No mu nkuru y’aba Adi (harimo isomo), ubwo twabohererezaga umuyaga ugumbahaye (usenya ntacyo usize)"
  51,42,Ntacyo wasigaga mu byo wahuraga nacyo utakigize umuyonga
  51,43,"No mu nkuru y’aba Thamudu (harimo isomo) ubwo babwirwaga bati \"Nimwishimishe by’igihe gito"
  51,44,"Ariko bigometse ku itegeko rya Nyagasani wabo, maze bakubitwa n’ikibatsi cy’umuriro w’inkuba bareba"
  51,45,Ntibashoboraga guhaguruka (ngo bahunge) cyangwa ngo bitabare
  51,46,"N’abantu ba Nuhu (ni uko twabagenje) mbere. Mu by’ukuri, bari abantu b’ibyigomeke"